  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Grill the fermented chestnuts for 10 minutes on each side.",
    "In a large pan, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped tomato and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Add the cauliflower and potatoes to the pan and cook for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the grilled chestnuts, garam masala, cumin, coriander, salt, and pepper to the pan and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
